英美小說選讀














 
科目名稱：英美小說選讀 (1)   授課教師：李健美  系別：英美語文學系  R專任  □兼任




開課班級

英美語文學系 3 年  合  班   □必修    R選修


學分數

2 學分 2 小時      


授課方式

R口頭講授   R分組討論   □媒體教學   □上機實習   
□其他（請詳述於後）


教學目標

This course aims to select modern short fiction of high literary quality and about fundamental human experiences which can be enjoyed and appreciated by students after textual, cultural and thematic analyses done in class.


教材課本

Sudden Fiction (Continued). Ed. Robert Shapard & James Thomas. New York: W.W. Norton & Company, 1996.


參考書籍

20th Century American Short Stories, Revised Edition, Volume 1, Jean A. McConochie. Boston, MA: Heinle, 1995.


教學進度
及內容

Week 1/ “The Unicorn in the Garden” (James Thurber) 
Week 2/ “My Life as A Bat” (Margaret Atwood)
Week 3/ “Grandma’s Tales” (Andrew Lam)
Week 4/ “The Flowers” (Alice Walker)
Week 5/ “The Liberation of Rome” (Robin Hemley)
Week 6/ “Sundress” (Terese Svoboda)
Week 7/ “Out on Bail” (Denis Johnson)
Week 8/ “The Writers’ Model” (Molly Giles)
Week 9/ Mid-term Exam
Week 10/ “We Meet At Last” (David Leavitt)
Week 11/ “The Unlikely Origin of Metaphor” (Richardo Pau-Llosa)
Week 12/ “Tergvinder’s Stone” (W. S. Merwin)
Week 13/ “Scheherazade” (Charles Baxter)
Week 14/ “Jacob’s Chicken” (Milos Macourek) 
Week 15/ “The Flood” (Joy Harjo)
Week 16/ “Doves” (Ursula Hegi)
Week 17/ “We Bad” (Salarrue)
Week 18/ Final Exam 


成績考核方式

平時考：30%、期中考：30%、期末考：40%
其他（如實習、報告、做作業、學習態度等，請說明於後並註明各項所佔百分比）


備考

1.  為鼓勵評分方式之多元化，避免僅以期中及期末考為評分依據，請詳述成績考核方式，並於開學時宣佈，以強化學習效果。
2.  本表應於開學前提交所屬學系或通識學部。




 


















